{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be corporate and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Innovate Solutions - SaaS</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #007bff;\n            --secondary-color: #e0e9f7;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-background: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), #0056b3);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            min-height: 400px;\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: white;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0e9f7;\n            color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        .features {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: left;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Innovate Solutions</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#features\">Features</a>\n        <a href=\"#pricing\">Pricing</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Streamline Your Business with Powerful SaaS</h2>\n        <p>Our innovative software solutions are designed to boost efficiency, enhance collaboration, and drive growth for your enterprise. Experience the future of business operations today.</p>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"features\" class=\"features\">\n        <h2>Key Features</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Seamless Integration</h3>\n                <p>Easily connect with your existing tools and workflows for a unified experience.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Scalable Performance</h3>\n                <p>Our platform grows with your business, ensuring you always have the resources you need.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Advanced Analytics</h3>\n                <p>Gain deep insights into your operations with comprehensive reporting and data visualization.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Robust Security</h3>\n                <p>Your data is protected with industry-leading security measures and compliance standards.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"pricing\" class=\"features\">\n        <h2>Flexible Pricing</h2>\n        <p>Choose a plan that best suits your needs. All plans include our core features and dedicated support.</p>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\" style=\"margin-top: 40px;\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Basic</h3>\n                <p>Ideal for small teams starting out. Access to essential features.</p>\n                <p><strong>$49</strong>/month</p>\n                <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">Choose Plan</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Pro</h3>\n                <p>For growing businesses needing advanced tools. Includes premium features.</p>\n                <p><strong>$99</strong>/month</p>\n                <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">Choose Plan</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Enterprise</h3>\n                <p>Custom solutions for large organizations. Scalable and tailored to your needs.</p>\n                <p><strong>Contact Us</strong></p>\n                <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"margin-top: 20px;\">Contact Sales</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Innovate Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Questions? Reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:info@innovatesolutions.com\">info@innovatesolutions.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}